&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p data-pid="XVVKbTQx"&gt;欧拉弹性线方程与单摆方程的等价性，后面有机会写一写。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p data-pid="cu8wrLFV"&gt;---------------------------------------------20230810--------------------------------------------&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-pid="fLCyOjkt"&gt;贴一个Auto07p的求解结果：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7fb877021a0ed854e1d9b127f2bdabb1_720w.jpg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="609" data-rawheight="480" data-watermark="original" data-original-src="v2-7fb877021a0ed854e1d9b127f2bdabb1" data-watermark-src="v2-e5d14de9a051bbb3e70573dba0cec919" data-private-watermark-src="v2-64a2244d12ab5b1be28c8af4e1bbe8d3" data-original-token="v2-7fb877021a0ed854e1d9b127f2bdabb1" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-pid="3HKHcTmw"&gt;纸张很长的时候，在屈曲较大时还可能出现多个周期的情况：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-482676416d940b4494d6179761c7d294_720w.png?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="609" data-rawheight="480" data-watermark="original" data-original-src="v2-482676416d940b4494d6179761c7d294" data-watermark-src="v2-655a6fac04f289b19b18fb3d38a1407f" data-private-watermark-src="v2-57ecb3d4001d74484a6d9ebe14e2ce00" data-original-token="v2-482676416d940b4494d6179761c7d294" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-pid="gSYepHVD"&gt;【参考文献】&lt;/p&gt;&lt;blockquote data-pid="tUCp78af"&gt;【1】Phys. Rev. Lett. &lt;b&gt;103&lt;/b&gt;, 174302&lt;br&gt;【2】Phys. Rev. Lett. &lt;b&gt;103&lt;/b&gt;, 174301 &lt;br&gt;【3】&lt;a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.sciencedirect.com/journal/extreme-mechanics-letters/vol/5/suppl/C" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;Volume 5&lt;/a&gt;,December 2015, Pages 81-87&lt;br&gt;【4】&lt;a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.springer.com/book/10.1007/978-3-319-50598-5" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;Modeling Nonlinear Problems in the Mechanics of Strings and Rods&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
